      "created_at": "2016-10-30T06:31:34.906Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/1X/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67\" title=\"IMG_2535.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67_2_800x600.JPG\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67_2_800x600.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67_2_1200x900.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67_2_1600x1200.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/7ee83fa5c888e77418227695b6b9846953846d67_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_2535.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">3264×2448 2.54 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Po vija rrotull një dyqani veshjesh këtu në Tiranë, kur vura re disa kravata mëndafshi me motive nga mozaikët e Butrintit, dritaret e Beratit dhe të tjera tema të trashëgimisë kulturore në Shqipëri, por jo vetëm. Kishte edhekravata me motive nga kohët tona, si njëra që bazohej tek i famshim “Pallati me shigjeta”, fotoja e fundit, kravata majtas. Shumë prej tyre mu dukën vërtet të bukura, dhe kishin paketimin që shpjegon nga vjen motivi i dizenjos dhe pak histori.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/1X/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f\" title=\"IMG_2533.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f_2_800x600.JPG\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f_2_800x600.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f_2_1200x900.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f_2_1600x1200.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/5c05ce6c3b5501900ac7c0ee2e464af98bf0a64f_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_2533.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">3264×2448 2.72 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Zbulova se prodhuesi është kompania Triqita, për të cilën nuk kisha dëgjuar më parë, por tek <a href=\"http://triqita.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">triqita.com</a> gjeta se kanë edhe të tjera produkte, gjithnjë me këtë mëndafshin me motivet e trashëgimisë.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/1X/8979ace7494ae45426ef44c0e252d4688b973963.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/8979ace7494ae45426ef44c0e252d4688b973963\" title=\"IMG_2534.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/8979ace7494ae45426ef44c0e252d4688b973963_2_800x600.JPG\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/8979ace7494ae45426ef44c0e252d4688b973963_2_800x600.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/8979ace7494ae45426ef44c